data.description: Welcome to a slice of paradise! Step into this exquisite home built in 2016, boasting just over 2,000 sq ft of pure comfort and luxury. Nestled on a serene half-acre lot, this gem is a country lover's dream, located on a quiet dead-end road. With its 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a spacious 3-car attached garage, this home is the epitome of modern elegance and convenience. As you walk through the inviting foyer, you'll find birch lockers that blend style and functionality, offering the perfect spot to keep things organized. Ascend the stairs to discover an open-concept kitchen, living, and dining area crowned by stunning cathedral ceilings. The kitchen, adorned with remarkable custom cabinets, is bathed in the gentle glow of dimmable lighting.,The dining area beckons you to a world of outdoor beauty, with a patio door leading to an upper deck overlooking a vast backyard adorned with trees, wildflowers, and occasional visits from local wildlife, because City of Wausau owns over 4 acres of land behind the property which currently provides a nature haven. Your very own firepit invites you to relish sunsets and nature's serene presence. On the main floor, you'll find a laundry area equipped with cabinets and motion lighting for added convenience. A full bath, a second bedroom, and the owner's suite with its expansive closet and walk-in shower complete this level. Both main floor bathrooms are now equipped with newly installed humidistats, ensuring optimal comfort. As you venture downstairs, you'll be greeted by two more bedrooms and yet another full bathroom with tasteful tile flooring and a tiled shower. The recently finished family room is bathed in natural light from dimmable cam lighting and large egress windows, offering ample space for family bonding and personal touches. The entire interior of the home has been freshly painted in appealing neutral colors, making it a blank canvas ready for your personal touch. This home has barely been lived in and feels as fresh as the day it was built. The garage provides more than enough space for your vehicles and storage needs. Don't miss the chance to experience country living while being just moments away from city convenience.
